{"tid":761544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人生仔冚家剷","createTime":"2018-07-30T12:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T00:59:05.000Z","uid":56698,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43b2f0137e6e9b7ec16b53f5e2812a28048cfdff","tid":761544,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"出世已住劏房 父愧對五歲兒 <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一家三口蝸居深水埗劏房的梁先生，輪候公屋五年仍上樓無望，對於房屋署擬提高輪候冊入息限額，勢必進一步延長輪候公屋時間，梁深感無奈，形容基層已遭政府離棄，「你有你講，佢有佢聽！」又慨嘆自己已年過半百，最歉疚是未能為五歲兒子提供比較理想的生活環境，「睇唔見前面，但亦只能夠係咁！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170301/00176_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170301%2F00176_003.html&d=ECuEBLj9%2FHVn5cERnK52mp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=04aa8bbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170301/00176_003.html</a>"},{"pid":"b759e9d3fb3b8898f59f421d58ca77e8fb26c6ea","tid":761544,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa730fc1124f9a1511b7f18d2386f668df9f282","tid":761544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821d262fba6fea2638021db440c698e84dcc66b7","tid":761544,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"重刷啦屌你老母戇鳩連登仔"},{"pid":"cf428dd39e98ad418b2c317bc5da220c65e4ac73","tid":761544,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680c1ab81a41f252ba09b2b223a24fab38a3c76a","tid":761544,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372e36